---
layout: layout.njk
title: Services
description: "Askia coaching services to land top tech roles."
metaTitle: "Coaching Services That Move Your Next Role | Askia"
metaDescription: "Outcome‑focused coaching services across resume, LinkedIn, interviews, and offer strategy."
breadcrumbs:
  - name: "Home"
    url: "/"
  - name: "Services"
    url: "/services/"
---
<section class="services-hero-new">
  <div class="container services-hero-grid">
    <div class="services-hero-copy">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Services</p>
      <h1 class="services-hero-title">{{ services.hero.title }}</h1>
      <p class="services-hero-subtitle">{{ services.hero.subtitle }}</p>
      <p class="services-hero-supporting">Pick a focused upgrade or build a full system. We’ll help you choose the fastest path.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="{{ services.hero.ctaLink }}">{{ services.hero.ctaLabel }}</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/resources/">View resources</a>
      </div>
      <div class="services-hero-metrics">
        <div><strong>7–14 days</strong><span>Typical delivery</span></div>
        <div><strong>2–6 weeks</strong><span>Coaching timelines</span></div>
        <div><strong>Signal-first</strong><span>Positioning system</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="services-hero-panel">
      <div class="services-hero-card">
        <strong>What clients choose first</strong>
        <p>Most start with a brand refresh, then add coaching as interviews begin.</p>
        <div class="services-hero-chips">
          <span>Resume upgrade</span>
          <span>LinkedIn signal</span>
          <span>Interview practice</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="services-hero-card accent">
        <strong>Outcomes you can feel</strong>
        <p>Clear positioning, interview momentum, and offer leverage.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section services-pillars">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pillar-header">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Service pillars</p>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Build signal at every stage</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Each service is designed to move you toward interviews and offers.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="services-pillar-grid">
      <div class="services-pillar">
        <strong>Signal</strong>
        <p>Positioning, resume, LinkedIn, and story architecture.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services-pillar">
        <strong>Momentum</strong>
        <p>Role targeting, outreach guidance, and interview preparation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services-pillar">
        <strong>Conversion</strong>
        <p>Offer strategy, negotiation, and decision support.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section services-grid">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pillar-header">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Core services</p>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Choose the path that fits your stage</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Start lean or go all‑in with a full brand rebuild.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="services-grid-cards" data-services-carousel>
      {% for tier in services.tiers %}
        <article class="services-card{% if tier.tag == 'Most Popular' %} is-featured{% endif %}">
          <span class="services-tag">{{ tier.tag }}</span>
          <h3>{{ tier.title }}</h3>
          <p class="services-price">{{ tier.price }}</p>
          <p>{{ tier.body }}</p>
          <ul>
            {% for bullet in tier.bullets %}
              <li>{{ bullet }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
          <div class="services-meta">
            <span>{{ tier.ideal }}</span>
            <span>{{ tier.turnaround }}</span>
          </div>
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-buy" href="{{ tier.buyLink }}">Buy now</a>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section services-precision">
  <div class="container services-precision-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Precision upgrades</p>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">High‑stakes moments, focused help</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Small, fast engagements when you need targeted leverage.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="{{ services.cta.ctaLink }}">Get a recommendation</a>
    </div>
    <div class="service-stack">
      <a class="service-tile" href="/cover-letter-writing/">
        <div class="service-header">
          <h3>Cover Letter Writing</h3>
          <span class="service-tag">Signal</span>
        </div>
        <p>Targeted narrative that earns the read.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="service-tile" href="/mock-interviews/">
        <div class="service-header">
          <h3>Mock Interviews</h3>
          <span class="service-tag">Execution</span>
        </div>
        <p>Live practice with real‑world feedback.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="service-tile" href="/career-clarity/">
        <div class="service-header">
          <h3>Career Clarity</h3>
          <span class="service-tag">Direction</span>
        </div>
        <p>Define the right role, level, and path.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="service-tile" href="/offer-strategy/">
        <div class="service-header">
          <h3>Offer Strategy</h3>
          <span class="service-tag">Leverage</span>
        </div>
        <p>Control timing, leverage, and total comp.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="service-tile" href="/ats-audit/">
        <div class="service-header">
          <h3>ATS Audit</h3>
          <span class="service-tag">Diagnostics</span>
        </div>
        <p>Find the blockers and fix them fast.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section services-role-tracks">
  <div class="container services-preview">
    <div>
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Role tracks</p>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Find a path built for your role</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Role tracks speak directly to how hiring works in your function.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/land-your-next-role/">Explore role tracks</a>
    </div>
    <div class="service-stack">
      <a class="service-tile" href="/software-engineer-career-coaching/">
        <div class="service-header">
          <h3>Software Engineer Coaching</h3>
          <span class="service-tag">SWE</span>
        </div>
        <p>System design and scope positioning.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="service-tile" href="/devops-career-coaching/">
        <div class="service-header">
          <h3>DevOps & SRE Coaching</h3>
          <span class="service-tag">DevOps</span>
        </div>
        <p>Reliability impact and infra leadership.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="service-tile" href="/data-career-coaching/">
        <div class="service-header">
          <h3>Data Career Coaching</h3>
          <span class="service-tag">Data</span>
        </div>
        <p>Business impact narratives for data roles.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="service-tile" href="/product-manager-career-coaching/">
        <div class="service-header">
          <h3>Product Manager Coaching</h3>
          <span class="service-tag">Product</span>
        </div>
        <p>Strategy, execution, and stakeholder signal.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="service-tile" href="/engineering-manager-coaching/">
        <div class="service-header">
          <h3>Engineering Manager Coaching</h3>
          <span class="service-tag">Leadership</span>
        </div>
        <p>Leadership scope and delivery systems.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container faq-stage">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">{{ services.faq.title }}</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Short, clear answers to the questions we hear most before someone books.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-grid">
      {% for item in services.faq.items %}
        <details class="faq-card">
          <summary>{{ item.question }}</summary>
          <p>{{ item.answer }}</p>
        </details>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container cta-band">
    <div>
      <h2 class="section-title">{{ services.cta.title }}</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">{{ services.cta.body }}</p>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="{{ services.cta.ctaLink }}">{{ services.cta.ctaLabel }}</a>
  </div>
</section>
